'''Nymeria''' is one of six [[direwolf]] cubs found by the children of [[House Stark]]. Nymeria is adopted and raised by [[Arya Stark]].

Arya named her after [[Nymeria]] of [[Dorne]], the warrior-queen of the [[Rhoynar]] who lived a thousand years ago.
